{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-60","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 60","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dodaj još jedan padajući izbornik nakon onog koji si nedavno postavio. Vrednost atributa elementa <code>id</code> treba da bude <code>lazy</code>, a vrednost atributa elementa <code>name</code> treba da bude isti kao poslednji padajući izbornik.</p>\n<p>Takođe dodajte element <code>label</code> sa desne strane novog padajućeg menija koji ima tekst <code>Lazy</code>. Uverite se da povezujete element <code>label</code> sa novim padajućim menijem koristeći atribut elementa <code>for</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804e3","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-60"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\"> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> <label for=\"loving\">Loving</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[43,45],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Morate dodati novi padajući meni.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('input[type=\"checkbox\"]'), 2);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš novi okvir za odabir mora imati atribut elementa <code>id</code> sa vrednošću <code>lazy</code> i atribut elementa <code>name</code> sa vrednošću <code>personality</code>. Proverite da postoji razmak nakon imena oznake za otvaranje i/ili da postoji razmak pre svih imena atributa elemenata.</p>","testString":"const checkboxes = [...document.querySelectorAll('input[type=\"checkbox\"]')];\nassert(\n  checkboxes.some(\n    (checkbox) =>\n      checkbox.id === 'lazy' && checkbox.getAttribute('name') === 'personality'\n  )\n);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoja nova kutijaška kutijačka treba da bude posle prve. Postavila si u pogređem redosledu.</p>","testString":"const checkboxes = [...document.querySelectorAll('input[type=\"checkbox\"]')].map(\n  (checkbox) => checkbox.id\n);\nassert(checkboxes.indexOf('loving') < checkboxes.indexOf('lazy'));"},{"text":"<p>Na desnoj strani vaše nove kutije za odabir, trebalo bi da postoji element sa tekstom <code>label</code> koji sadrži tekst <code>Lazy</code>.</p>","testString":"const nextElementSibling = document.querySelectorAll('input[type=\"checkbox\"]')?.[1]?.nextElementSibling;\nassert.isOk(nextElementSibling?.nodeName === 'LABEL' && nextElementSibling?.innerText?.replace(/\\s+/g, '')?.match(/^Lazy$/i)\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>label</code> novi mora imati atribut elementa <code>for</code> sa istom vrednošću kao svojstvo elementa <code>id</code> novog kontrolnog polja za izbor. Možda ste ostavili tu vrednost ili napravili pravopisnu grešku.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(\n  document.querySelectorAll('input[type=\"checkbox\"]')?.[1]?.nextElementSibling?.getAttribute('for'),\n    'lazy'\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-60","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required"